data.description: Meticulosely maintained and renovated 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with an inground POOL on a HALF ACRE with all the upgrades. Featuring a new roof, new AC, new water heater, stainless steel appliances, upgraded electrical panel with whole house generator and solar panel system. Home features tile flooring and an open concept split bedroom floor plan. Hurricane transparent shutters on all windows to keep you safe during the hurricane season.
